properties.name: Color
properties.expression: thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Upper Rounding') < 0 ? thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Color') : thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Start Color')

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;const US = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Upper Split') * 0.01;const val = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Start Width') * widthScale * scaleFactor * (1-US) + (US * thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Width') * widthScale * scaleFactor);[val, val * thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Upper Rounding') * 0.01]

properties.name: Rotation
properties.expression: const mynormal = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke Group').content('Path 1').path.normalOnPath(thisLayer.clamp(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper').content('Upper Stroke Group').content('Trim Paths 1').end * 0.01, 0.0001, 0.999));thisLayer.radiansToDegrees(Math.atan2(mynormal[1],mynormal[0]))

properties.name: End Width
properties.expression: const C1 = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Start Width');const US = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Upper Split') * 0.01;(C1 * (1 - US) + (US * thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Width'))) / C1 * 100

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function upperStrokePath() {        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.scale[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.anchorPoint.value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.position.value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos], [[0, 0], thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1)], false);        }    }upperStrokePath();

properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Start Width') * scaleFactor * widthScale;

properties.name: End Width
properties.expression: thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Width') / thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Start Width') * 100;

properties.name: Color
properties.expression: thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Lower Rounding') < 0 ? thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('End Color') : thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Color')

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;const LS = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Lower Split') * 0.01;const val = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Width') * scaleFactor * widthScale * (1 - LS) + (LS * thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('End Width') *scaleFactor * widthScale);[val, val * thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Lower Rounding') * 0.01]

properties.name: Rotation
properties.expression: const mynormal = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower').content('Middle Stroke Group').content('Path 1').path.normalOnPath(thisLayer.clamp(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower').content('Middle Stroke Group').content('Trim Paths 1').end * 0.01, 0.0001, 0.999));thisLayer.radiansToDegrees(Math.atan2(mynormal[1],mynormal[0]))

properties.name: End Width
properties.expression: const C2 = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Width');const C3 = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('End Width');const LS = thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Lower Split') * 0.01;(C2 * (1 - LS) + (LS * C3)) / C2 *100

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function lowerStrokePath() {        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.scale[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p3ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.anchorPoint.value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.position.value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p3ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [inTangPos, [0, 0]], [thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1), [0, 0]], false);        }    }lowerStrokePath();

properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Width') * scaleFactor * widthScale;

properties.name: End Width
properties.expression: thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('End Width') / thisLayer.effect('Tapered Stroke')('Middle Width') * 100;
